'''热带风暴艾米莉'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Emily}}）是2011年8月一场强度虽弱，但却在[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]北部大部分地区降下瓢泼大雨的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]，也是[[2011年大西洋飓风季|同年大西洋飓风季]]第五场获得命名的风暴。系统源自7月下旬在大西洋开放水域行进多日的一股强度较高，但结构杂乱无章的[[东风波|东风波]]。8月1日，系统结构在逼近[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]后已略有改善，令群岛多地天气恶劣。两天后，这股扰动天气发展出闭合环流中心，热带风暴艾米莉至此成型。气旋继续在加勒比地区行进，总体结构依然混乱，但却在沿途产生强烈[[雷暴|雷暴]]天气和阵风。8月4日，艾米莉微弱的对流已被[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]的山区地形扰乱，气象机构认为系统已不再属于热带气旋。8月6日离开加勒比地区东北部海域后，风暴残留一度再生成热带风暴，最终于次日逐渐消散。

虽然结构混乱，但艾米莉却对多个加勒比海国家和地区构成重大破坏。小安的列斯群岛各地都有树木倒塌，并因暴雨引发大面积洪灾，不过只有[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]灾情较为严重，该国有一人遇难。[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]也发生大范围洪涝灾害，对居民和道路构成影响，当地[[基础设施|基础设施]]遭受的破坏总额约为500万美元。风暴消散后的残留还在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛大部分地区产生旷日持续的降雨，[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]发生大面积洪灾和[[泥石流|泥石流]]，致使7000余人流离失所，首都[[圣多明哥|圣多明哥]]有三人溺毙。邻近的[[海地|海地]][[阿蒂博尼特省|阿蒂博尼特省]]有数以百计民房被淹，居民被迫疏散。该国南部半岛只出现轻度风害，但有一人丧生。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Emily 2011 track.png}}
热带风暴艾米莉的成因较为复杂，可以从8月初追溯至7月下旬。2011年7月下旬，有[[东风波|东风波]]内嵌在[[季风槽|季风槽]]内离开非洲西岸<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107260605.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-26 | accessdate = 2016-05-14 | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|National Weather Service]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | last = Tichacek | first = Mike | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071549/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107260605.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] }}</ref>。受北侧的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，东风波朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向经过[[大西洋|大西洋]]开放海域，其环流范围广阔，但有一至两天几乎没有产生[[降水|降水]]<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065654/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL052011_Emily.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL052011_Emily.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | title = Tropicical Cyclone Report Tropical Storm Emily (AL052011): 2–7 August 2011 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2012-01-13 | accessdate = 2016-05-14 | first1 = Todd B | last1 = Kimberlain | first2 = John P. | last2 = Cangialosi | location = Miami, FL }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107270554.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-27 | accessdate = 2016-05-14 | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Tichacek | first = Mike | location = Miami, FL | format = TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071206/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107270554.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。随着时间的推移，广阔的系统周围有[[对流|对流]]带持续增长，于7月30日发展出两个明显的环流中心<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107280617.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-28 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Tichacek | first = Mike | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107280617.txt | format = TXT }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Weather Service | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107282347.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107282347.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-29 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Formosa | first = Mike | deadurl = no | format = TXT | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。7月31日早上，大范围低气压区的结构已有显著改善，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]称系统即将成为[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107310544/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-07-31 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Berg | first = Robbie | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306134935/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107310544/index.php?basin=atl | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。但到了下午，系统的主环流逐渐拉开，并且最西侧部分很快分离并形成另一股东风波<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041518/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201108010001.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201108010001.txt | location = Miami, FL | publisher = National Weather Service | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | work = National Hurricane Center | first = Jeffrey | last = Lewitsky | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref>。新生成的扰动天气内包含范围广阔但较为分散的对流和[[雨带|雨带]]，并短暂对[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]构成影响<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107312058/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-07-31 | accessdate = 2011-08-01 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | first1 = James | first2 = Michael | last2 = Brennan | last1 = Franklin | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060732/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107312058/index.php?basin=atl | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。次日，环流结构有所改善，带有新深层对流区的中心在系统内占据主导地位。经过[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]期间，系统结构进一步改善，[[最大持续风速|地面风速]]已提升至接近热带风暴水平<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306135253/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201108011424/index.php?basin=atl | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201108011424/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2011-08-01 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no }}</ref>。飞入系统的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机发现，深层对流附近已存在层次分明的环流中心。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月2日凌晨0点，气象机构直接把[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]以南的系统归类成热带风暴，并以“艾米莉”（{{lang|en|Emily}}）命名。受北侧的强烈[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，气旋起初加速朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动。<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number One | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Brennan | first = Michael | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404073712/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>

[[File:Emily_Aug_3_2011_1750Z.jpg|thumb]]附近的热带风暴艾米莉]]

根据气象部门推算，风暴前方大气环境较为干燥，所以只会逐渐增强，直至经过[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]<ref>{{cite report | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number Two | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Brennan | first = Michael | archivedate = 2016-04-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403203556/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月2日，气旋发展出[[雨带|带状特征]]，强度和组织结构波动幅度都很小<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.003.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number Three | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Brennan | first = Michael | archive-date = 2021-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210112084304/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.003.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此后，艾米莉的[[气象卫星|卫星图像]]变得更清晰，发展出不规则的[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]，美国国家飓风中心估计气旋于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月3日凌晨0点达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]80公里的最高强度<ref name="TCR" />。即便是到了这个时候，侦察机的观测结果表明风暴环流依然混乱，多个预测模型甚至认为艾米莉会在[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]前消散<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number Four | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220558/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.004.shtml? | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Avila | first = Lixion | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。受上层[[风切变|风切变]]增多影响，气旋的最深层对流同环流中心剥离，并且此后再也没有恢复原有状态<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number Five | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.005.shtml? | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Brennan | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403013819/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.005.shtml | first = Michael | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-04-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404012534/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.008.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number Eight | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Lixion | first = Avila | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。8月4日，风暴上空的上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]扩张，云层格局及对流带层次都有改善<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.012.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number Twelve | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Lixion | first = Avila | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404020810/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.012.shtml | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。艾米莉继续行进至[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]以南近海<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404012349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.public.012.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.public.012.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Advisory Number Twelve | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Lixion | first = Avila }}</ref>，本已脆弱的环流在附近垂直风切变增多及山区地形的共同影响下变得越来越混乱。气旋加速穿越伊斯帕尼奥拉岛，于{{lang|en|UTC}}夜间21点左右退化成开放式低压槽。<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | location = Miami, FL | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Lixion | first = Avila | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.013.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160401183700/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.013.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Emily Advisory Number Thirteen | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-04-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

艾米莉的残留低压槽继续向西北方向进入[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]海域，气象部门认为这里的上层风切变较少，所以风暴有望重新发展<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201108052344/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100530/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201108052344/index.php?basin=atl | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。接下来几天里，系统进入巴哈马上空，并继续朝东面的[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]南部逼近。8月6日晚，低压槽发展出新环流中心，到{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点已在[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]附近重新成为弱热带低气压。六小时后，艾米莉再度达到热带风暴标准，但很快就因风切变增多而于次日消退成残留低气压区。<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160401183700/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al05/al052011.discus.013.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Emily Advisory Number Fourteen | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2011-08-07 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last1 = Brennan | first1 = Michael | last2 = Stewart | first2 = Stacy | archivedate = 2016-04-01 }}</ref>低气压区转向东北偏东并加速前进，绕过[[百慕大|百慕大]]后向东面的大西洋开放水域移动。接下来系统再度发展出带有深层对流的大范围烈风强度风场，促使美国国家飓风中心继续监控。<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | last = Pasch | first = Richard | date = 2011-08-09 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065643/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201108090532/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201108090532 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201108090532/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201108090532 }}</ref>受强烈风切变及本身移动速度过快的共同影响，系统残留无法出现显著发展，最终于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月11日中午12点左右在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以西约1565公里洋面完全消散<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
由于系统很可能发展成热带气旋，[[法国气象局|法国气象局]]向[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]和马提尼克发出黄色气旋警报，称当地有可能马上受到狂风袭击<ref>{{cite report | title = Météo: la Martinique en alerte jaune cyclone | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | last = Saint-Joseph | work = kelDOM | publisher = COMantilles | first = Leïla | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234950/http://www.domactu.com/actualite/18181999436253/martinique-meteo-la-martinique-en-alerte-jaune-cyclone/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.domactu.com/actualite/18181999436253/martinique-meteo-la-martinique-en-alerte-jaune-cyclone/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = METEO: Alerte jaune cyclonique | date = 2011-07-31 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | work = France-Antilles | author = Staff writer | publisher = France Antilles Martinique | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002530/http://www.guadeloupe.franceantilles.fr/actualite/education-sante-environnement/meteo-alerte-jaune-cyclonique-31-07-2011-133156.php | url = http://www.guadeloupe.franceantilles.fr/actualite/education-sante-environnement/meteo-alerte-jaune-cyclonique-31-07-2011-133156.php }}</ref>。面临风暴来袭，波多黎各宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="Brownsville1">{{cite news |author=Daniel Trenton |agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |publisher=Freedom Communications |work=The Brownsville Herald |date=2011-08-03 |accessdate=2016-05-15 |title=Haiti is next for Tropical Storm Emily |archivedate=2011-08-03 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.brownsvilleherald.com/news/us_world/article_728ee123-7afa-576d-b876-1cc326ca9581.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60fHNZMf3?url=http://www.brownsvilleherald.com/articles/haiti-129533-storm-tropical.html }}</ref>。政府官员下令准备超过400个风暴避难所，并确保供水充足<ref name="ElNuevoDia1" />。气旋袭击当天早上，政府工作人员放假回家，法庭也予关闭<ref name="ElNuevoDia1">{{cite news | title = No hay trabajo en el Gobierno de Puerto Rico mañana | work = El Nuevo Día | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | author = Staff reporter | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/noticias/locales/nota/nohaytrabajoenelgobiernodepuertorico-1029551/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104165123/http://www.elnuevodia.com/nohaytrabajoenelgobiernodepuertoricomanana-1029551.html }}</ref>。[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]发布通告，建议波多黎各和[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]在艾米莉过境前不要下海游泳或划船休闲<ref name="USCG 1">{{cite news | title = Coast Guard urges mariners to exercise caution, prepare for tropical storm conditions in Puerto Rico, U.S. Virgin Islands | date = 2011-08-02 | publisher = [[美国海岸警卫队|United States Coast Guard]] | accessdate = 2011-08-02 | archivedate = 2012-03-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120324053604/http://www.d7.uscgnews.com/go/doc/586/1152319/ | url = http://www.uscgnews.com/go/doc/4007/1403227/Coast-Guard-urges-mariners-to-exercise-caution-prepare-for-tropical-storm-conditions-in-Puerto-Rico-U-S-Virgin-Islands }}</ref>。因天气恶劣，[[捷蓝航空|捷蓝航空]]决定免收前往[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]的航班机票费用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jetblue.com/JetblueAlerts/WeatherUpdate.aspx |archivedate=2011-08-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60eRiexrj?url=http://www.jetblue.com/JetblueAlerts/WeatherUpdate.aspx |title=Operations Update |date=2011-08-02 |publisher=[[捷蓝航空|JetBlue Airways]] |accessdate=2011-08-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[海洋绿洲号|海洋绿洲号]]、[[海洋自由号|海洋自由号]]、[[嘉年华之梦号|嘉年华之梦号]]和[[嘉年华自由号|嘉年华自由号]]邮轮变更航线，以期避开风暴<ref>{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Emily scatters cruise ships in the Caribbean | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2014-01-05 | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | last = Sloan | first = Gene | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140105072340/http://travel.usatoday.com/cruises/post/2011/08/tropical-storm-emily-eastern-caribbean-cruises/179709/1 | publisher = Gannett Company | archivedate = 2014-01-05 | deadurl = yes | url = http://travel.usatoday.com/cruises/post/2011/08/tropical-storm-emily-eastern-caribbean-cruises/179709/1 }}</ref>。

[[海地|海地]]曾于2010年1月发生[[2010年海地地震|重大地震]]，艾米莉来袭时，仍有约63万人住在帐篷里。由于各地都缺少稳固的建筑供人们躲避，气旋经过的消息在该国引起恐慌。国内应急官员动用22辆大客车，将生活在洪水易发区域的数千居民转移，还敦促居民储存食品并保管好个人财物。[[联合国|联合国]]要求驻该国的1万1500名军人待命，准备在有必要的情况下协助救灾工作。[[红十字会与红新月会国际联合会|红十字会与红新月会国际联合会]]也要求多支应急工作组待命，准备在之前已救助12万5000人的基础上提供包括食品在内的进一步救灾援助。<ref name="Brownsville1" />风暴来袭前，有关部门将国内所有机场及其它飞机降落点关闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Situation Report Haiti Operation August 2011 | date = 2011-08-31 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = ReliefWeb | author = Logistics Cluster | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305160601/http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/situation-report-haiti-operation-august-2011 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/situation-report-haiti-operation-august-2011 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

