=== 小安的列斯群岛 ===
强烈的雨带在马提尼克产生阵风和暴雨，降雨总量达到150毫米<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223914/http://geodata.us/weather/show.php?usaf=789250&uban=99999&m=8&c=Martinique&y=2011 | url = http://geodata.us/weather/show.php?usaf=789250&uban=99999&m=8&c=Martinique&y=2011 | title = Weather in LAMENTIN AERO August 2011, Martinique | publisher = Geodata.us | year = 2011 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>，引发街道洪灾，还有部分民居被淹。风暴期间岛上有约5000居民失去供电，<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[法新社|AFP]]; France 2 | publisher = France Télévisions | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2012-03-28 | title = Tempête Emily: un mort à la Martinique | archivedate = 2012-03-28 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120328112741/http://info.france2.fr/planete/tempete-tropicale-emily-la-guadeloupe-en-alerte-69883664.html | url = http://info.france2.fr/planete/tempete-tropicale-emily-la-guadeloupe-en-alerte-69883664.html }}</ref>但停电范围基本局限在该岛东南部，并且很快便已恢复。首府[[法兰西堡|法兰西堡]]因土壤含水过度饱和发生严重[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，当地约40户家庭被迫转移。<ref>{{cite news | title = Martinique/tempête: un mort électrocuté | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | work = Le Figaro | publisher = Dassault Group | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080643/http://www.lefigaro.fr/flash-actu/2011/08/02/97001-20110802FILWWW00443-martiniquetempete-un-mort-electrocute.php | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.lefigaro.fr/flash-actu/2011/08/02/97001-20110802FILWWW00443-martiniquetempete-un-mort-electrocute.php }}</ref>该市共有29套房屋被洪水淹没<ref>{{cite news | title = Fort-de-France durement touché par la tempête Emily | agency = Agence France-Presse | work = Le Point | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2011-08-04 | publisher = Artémis | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060939/http://www.lepoint.fr/monde/fort-de-france-durement-touche-par-la-tempete-emily-03-08-2011-1359268_24.php | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.lepoint.fr/monde/fort-de-france-durement-touche-par-la-tempete-emily-03-08-2011-1359268_24.php }}</ref>，导致一名男子因电缆漏电触电身亡<ref name="LeXpress.">{{cite news | title = Tempête Emily: un mort en Martinique | date = 2011-08-02 | work = L'Express | agency = Agence France-Presse | first = Dominique | last = Chomereau-Lamotte | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110104/http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/meteo/tempete-emily-un-mort-en-martinique_1017388.html | url = http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/meteo/tempete-emily-un-mort-en-martinique_1017388.html | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

艾米莉在瓜德罗普产生的破坏程度不高，强烈阵风将多棵树木连根拔起，还令[[巴斯特尔岛|巴斯特尔岛]]街道上到处都是各种垃圾。风暴期间当地一条道路临时封闭，以防万一，但气旋过后很快便恢复通车<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212504/http://www.guadeloupe.franceantilles.fr/actualite/education-sante-environnement/tempete-emily-premiers-bilans-en-guadeloupe-02-08-2011-133385.php | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.guadeloupe.franceantilles.fr/actualite/education-sante-environnement/tempete-emily-premiers-bilans-en-guadeloupe-02-08-2011-133385.php | title = Tempête Emily : premiers bilans en Guadeloupe | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | work = France-Antilles | author = Staff writer | publisher = France Antilles Martinique }}</ref>。[[圣克里斯多福与尼维斯|圣克里斯多福与尼维斯]]部分电缆在烈风强度风力影响下中断，导致两岛全面停电<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305021402/http://www.thestkittsnevisobserver.com/2011/07/29/ts-emily.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.thestkittsnevisobserver.com/2011/07/29/ts-emily.html | title = Tropical Storm Emily brings high winds, rain to the region | work = The St. Kitts-Nevis Observer | publisher = St. Kitts-Nevis Publishing Association | author = Staff writer | date = 2011-08-02 | accessdate = 2016-03-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。气旋令[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]上空的大气变得更加湿润，当地出现间歇性的暴雨，但局部降雨总量基本没有超过25毫米。群岛风速也不高，测得的最强阵风时速约为83公里。<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20120718170245/http://virginislandsdailynews.com/news/emily-passes-to-south-has-little-impact-on-v-i-1.1183666 |deadurl=yes |url=http://virginislandsdailynews.com/news/emily-passes-to-south-has-little-impact-on-v-i-1.1183666 |title=Emily passes to south, has little impact on V.I. |date=2011-08-03 |accessdate=2012-07-18 |last=Blackburn |first=Joy |newspaper=The Virgin Islands Daily News |publisher=Times-Shamrock Communications |archivedate=2012-07-18 }}</ref>

=== 波多黎各 ===
艾米莉在波多黎各附近的移动速度非常缓慢，岛上多地因此长时间受到风暴影响。该州南部的降水最多，[[卡瓜斯|卡瓜斯]]风暴期间的降雨总量达209毫米。<ref name="TCR" />[[输电网路|输电网路]]因狂风受损，约有1万8500用户失去供电，还有约6000人在风暴期间失去饮水供应<ref name="power">{{cite news | title = Emily fue un ensayo | newspaper = El Nuevo Día | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | first = Gerardo E. | last = Alvarado-León | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/noticias/locales/nota/emilyfueunensayo-1030317/ | archivedate = 2016-05-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160507014554/http://www.elnuevodia.com/noticias/locales/nota/emilyfueunensayo-1030317/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。数十人撤至避难所，其中大部分是生活在高危地区附近的居民<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160513012647/http://www.elnuevodia.com/noticias/locales/nota/casi30refugiadostraselpasodeemilyporlaisla-1031690/ | title = Casi 30 refugiados tras el paso de Emily por la Isla | newspaper = El Nuevo Día | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2011-08-05 | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | last = Menchaca | first = Jerohim O. | deadurl = no | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/noticias/locales/nota/casi30refugiadostraselpasodeemilyporlaisla-1031690/ | archivedate = 2016-05-13 }}</ref>。部分区域降雨量达250毫米<ref name="herald">{{cite news | archivedate = 2011-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110829143351/http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/08/05/2347170/flooding-from-emily-kills-4.html | url = http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/08/05/2347170/flooding-from-emily-kills-4.html | title = Flooding from Emily kills 4 | publisher = The McClatchy Company | newspaper = The Miami Herald | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2011-08-29 | first1 = Curtis | last1 = Morgan | first2 = Frances | last2 = Robles | first3 = Amelie | last3 = Baron | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，致使三条河流泛滥成灾，31号和{{lang|en|I}}-3号公路交汇路段被淹后暂时封闭<ref name="power" />。受山体滑坡等因素影响，岛上各地还有多条道路无法通行<ref name="sigue">{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-09-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925071542/http://www.elnuevodia.com/emilysiguelasincidenciasminutoaminuto-1030671.html | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/noticias/locales/nota/emilysiguelasincidenciasminutoaminuto-1030671/ | title = Emily: Sigue las incidencias minuto a minuto | newspaper = El Nuevo Día | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | author = Staff reporter }}</ref>。估初步估算，全岛的[[基础设施|基础设施]]一共受到价值500万美元的破坏<ref>{{cite news |last=Alcaide |first=Maria D. |title=Pérdidas de $5 millones en carreteras |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004160826/http://www.primerahora.com/perdidasde%245millonesencarreteras-532734.html |archivedate=2012-10-04 |url=http://www.primerahora.com/perdidasde$5millonesencarreteras-532734.html |date=2011-08-05 |accessdate=2012-10-04 |work=Primera Hora |publisher=Grupo Ferré-Rangel }}</ref>。岛上约有28万雇员（占劳动力总数的三成）停工两天，对地方经济构成重大影响，资本流失估算达5500万美元<ref>{{cite news | title = El cese de operaciones del Gobierno por "Emily" acarreó pérdidas millonarias | author = EFE | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | work = La Prensa | publisher = La Prensa Foundation | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812210620/http://www.laprensasa.com/25_hispanos/1218630_el-cese-de-operaciones-del-gobierno-por-emily-acarreo-perdidas-millonarias.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.laprensasa.com/25_hispanos/1218630_el-cese-de-operaciones-del-gobierno-por-emily-acarreo-perdidas-millonarias.html }}</ref>。

[[圣洛伦索_(波多黎各)|圣洛伦索]]一座桥梁受到重创，有倒塌的风险，导致25户家庭与世隔绝<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.primerahora.com/residentespreocupadosporcondiciondepuenteensanlorenzo-532579.html | deadurl = no | title = Residentes preocupados por condición de puente en San Lorenzo | last = Cancel | first = Alex F. | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2012-10-04 | work = Primera Hora | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | archivedate = 2012-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004161143/http://www.primerahora.com/residentespreocupadosporcondiciondepuenteensanlorenzo-532579.html }}</ref>。[[塞瓦_(波多黎各)|塞瓦]]有多户民宅被淹，街道陷入混乱，还有一片住宅区的大门倒塌<ref>{{cite news | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2012-10-04 | work = Primera Hora | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | author = Staff writer | url = http://www.primerahora.com/alcaldedeceibainformadedanosporculpadeemily-532039.html | title = Alcalde de Ceiba informa de daños por culpa de Emily | archivedate = 2012-10-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004161237/http://www.primerahora.com/alcaldedeceibainformadedanosporculpadeemily-532039.html }}</ref>。当地农业也受到风暴影响，[[亚武科阿|亚武科阿]]有490公顷[[香蕉|香蕉]]苗被暴雨冲毁<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004161412/http://www.primerahora.com/evaluanlaszonasafectadasporemily-532733.html | url = http://www.primerahora.com/evaluanlaszonasafectadasporemily-532733.html | title = Evalúan las zonas afectadas por Emily | last1 = Rosa | first1 = Bárbara J. F. | last2 = Cancel | first2 = Alex F. | last3 = Saavedra | first3 = Maelo V. | last4 = Doll | first4 = Sara J. | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2012-10-04 | work = Primera Hora | publisher = Grupo Ferré-Rangel | archivedate = 2012-10-04 }}</ref>。

