=== 伊斯帕尼奥拉岛 ===
虽然结构混乱，但艾米莉及其残留还是令[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]普降暴雨，降雨量最高的[[内巴|内巴]]高达528毫米。严重洪灾及多起[[泥石流|泥石流]]等因素共同影响，致使56个社区同外界的交通中断。<ref name="hoy">{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120319002737/http://www.hoy.com.do/el-pais/2011/8/5/387356/Lluvias-dejan-3-muertos-y-7000-evacuados | url = http://www.hoy.com.do/el-pais/2011/8/5/387356/Lluvias-dejan-3-muertos-y-7000-evacuados | title = Lluvias dejan 3 muertos y 7.000 evacuados | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2012-03-19 | agency = Associated Press | work = Hoy | publisher = Periódico Hoy | archivedate = 2012-03-19 }}</ref>风暴导致该国7534人无家可归，其中有1549人前往风暴避难所躲避<ref>{{cite news | first1 = Soila | last1 = Paniagua | first2 = Ivelisse | last2 = Rosario | title = Emily deja 7,534  desplazados y a 47 comunidades aisladas | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2012-03-19 | publisher = Periódico Hoy | work = Hoy | url = http://www.hoy.com.do/el-pais/2011/8/4/387283/Emily-deja-7534-desplazados-y-a-47-comunidades-aisladas | archivedate = 2012-03-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120319002744/http://www.hoy.com.do/el-pais/2011/8/4/387283/Emily-deja-7534-desplazados-y-a-47-comunidades-aisladas }}</ref>。持续数小时的降水导致部分河流泛滥成灾，但没有对附近地区构成重大破坏<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120325043135/http://www.elnacional.com.do/nacional/2011/8/5/90905/Remanentes-tormenta-Emily-aun-se-sienten | publisher = Ahora! Publications | accessdate = 2012-03-25 | newspaper = El Nacional | first = Teofilo | last = Bonilla | url = http://www.elnacional.com.do/nacional/2011/8/5/90905/Remanentes-tormenta-Emily-aun-se-sienten | title = Remanentes tormenta Emily aún se sienten | date = 2011-08-05 | archivedate = 2012-03-25 }}</ref>。狂风令海上波涛汹涛，对船只运作及海滨住宅产生影响，但持续时间很短<ref name="hoy" />。[[圣多明哥|圣多明哥]]东部有两名男子被暴涨的河水卷走后溺亡，该市另外还有一人因洪灾丧生<ref>{{cite news | title = Emily deja tres muertos en Dominicana | publisher = Compañía Periodística Nacional | newspaper = El Universal | agency = Associated Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073604/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/784017.html | date = 2011-08-05 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/784017.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。

艾米莉于8月11日中午消散，与多米尼加相邻的海地因此没有遭受之前预计的灾难性破坏。风暴期间，[[雅克梅勒|雅克梅勒]]和泰巴尔（{{lang|en|Tabarre}}）至少有235人需要撤离，[[戈纳伊夫|戈纳伊夫]]和[[米拉瓜纳|米拉瓜纳]]也有65名囚犯需要转移<ref name="herald" />。[[阿蒂博尼特省|阿蒂博尼特省]]民防工作组将约300居民疏散<ref name="herald" />。降水引发洪灾，该国有超过300 户民房受损，另有多家[[霍乱|霍乱]]治疗中心被毁<ref name="degats">{{cite web | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160504045340/http://www.parismatch.com/Actu/International/Haiti-Degats-limites-apres-le-passage-de-la-tempete-tropicale-Emily-150411 | newspaper = Paris Match | publisher = Lagardère Group | last = Innocent | url = http://www.parismatch.com/Actu/International/Haiti-Degats-limites-apres-le-passage-de-la-tempete-tropicale-Emily-150411 | title = Haïti. Dégats limités après le passage d'Emily | first = Clerna | date = 2011-08-05 | archivedate = 2016-05-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。为了应对疫情再度爆发的风险，有关部门向水源可能遭污染的地区派发特制消毒器<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=yes |title=Local company sanitizing water in Haiti |author=WZZM Channel 13 |work=[[美国广播公司|ABC]] |publisher=Gannett Company |date=2011-08-05 |accessdate=2013-02-09 |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130209212447/http://www.wzzm13.com/news/article/174463/2/Local-company-sanitizing-water-in-Haiti- |archivedate=2013-02-09 |url=http://www.wzzm13.com/news/article/174463/2/Local-company-sanitizing-water-in-Haiti- }}</ref>。人们在[[莱凯|莱凯]]附近的山沟里找到一具尸体，但无法确定其死因，当地另有一人被倒塌的树木所伤<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.lapresse.ca/international/amerique-latine/201108/05/01-4423938-haiti-la-tempete-emily-a-fait-un-mort-et-de-nombreuses-familles-sinistrees.php | title = Haïti: la tempête Emily a fait un mort et de nombreuses familles sinistrées | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160508065908/http://www.lapresse.ca/international/amerique-latine/201108/05/01-4423938-haiti-la-tempete-emily-a-fait-un-mort-et-de-nombreuses-familles-sinistrees.php | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = Group Gesca | newspaper = La Presse | agency = Agence France-Presse | archivedate = 2016-05-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。狂风还在[[莱奥甘|莱奥甘]]和雅克梅勒造成部分财物受损<ref name="degats" />。

=== 其它地区 ===
风暴残留形成的低压槽在[[古巴|古巴]]东部产生倾盆大雨，致使多条河流泛滥。[[圣地亚哥-德古巴|圣地亚哥-德古巴]]发生破坏性的洪灾，不但淹没多条道路，还令37套民宅被淤泥覆盖。<ref>{{cite news | title = Onda tropical causa inundaciones y daños en Santiago, Cuba | date = 2011-08-07 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | publisher = TeleSUR | archivedate = 2012-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402223329/http://multimedia.telesurtv.net/media/telesur.video.web/telesur-web/ | deadurl = no | url = http://videos.telesurtv.net/video/44724/onda-tropical-causa-inundaciones-y-danos-en-santiago-cuba }}</ref>系统之后再度发展成热带低气压，又在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]产生旷日持久的降雨，大巴哈马岛及周边海域因此收到强烈雷暴警告<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=11999 | newspaper = The Nassau Guardian | first = K. | last = Nancoo-Russel | title = Emily drenches GB with persistent rains | date = 2011-08-08 | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | archivedate = 2014-10-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018101605/http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=11999 }}</ref>，测得的降雨总量达200毫米<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Season 2011: Tropical Storm Emily (Caribbean Sea) | publisher = NASA | date = 2011-08-10 | first = Rob | last = Gutro | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214545/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2011/h2011_Emily.html | url = http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2011/h2011_Emily.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

